Linkable has forged partnerships with the leading payment networks to pioneer the use of credit cards, debit cards and digital payment accounts as a universal loyalty identifier. Since the beginning, these partners have worked closely with us to enable a new way for shoppers to be rewarded for loyalty and simplify the process of coupon redemption in a fully digital environment that spans online and offline. See our partners…








