Innovation isn’t just a great idea. It’s also brilliant execution. Since our founding, we have been focused on changing the way consumers, brands and retailers connect. That meant breaking some rules and changing the molds. Along the way, we developed some amazing concepts that were recognized and rewarded with patents. We are proud of the team of innovators that drove these patents and are the foundation of our platform.








