Linkable Networks, Inc.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 25, 2017 8:46 PM ET
Internet Software and Services

Company Overview of Linkable Networks, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Linkable Networks, Inc. develops and offers SaaS-based shopper attribution platform that enables retailers and brand marketers to measure the return on advertisement spend of any media channel on in-store sales based on actual consumer transactions. The company provides Linkable Promotions, a solution for connecting digital incentives to consumer credit, debit, and pre-paid cards through card-linked offers; Linkable Media, a solution for in-store attribution of digital media based on consumer purchases; and Omnyverse, a self-service network enabling advertisers to deliver performance-based offers through publishers that can be redeemed in-store. It has strategic partnerships with American Ex...
Linkable Networks, Inc. develops and offers SaaS-based shopper attribution platform that enables retailers and brand marketers to measure the return on advertisement spend of any media channel on in-store sales based on actual consumer transactions. The company provides Linkable Promotions, a solution for connecting digital incentives to consumer credit, debit, and pre-paid cards through card-linked offers; Linkable Media, a solution for in-store attribution of digital media based on consumer purchases; and Omnyverse, a self-service network enabling advertisers to deliver performance-based offers through publishers that can be redeemed in-store. It has strategic partnerships with American Express, MasterCard, PayPal, and Visa. The company was formerly known as Clovr Media, Inc. and changed its name to Linkable Networks, Inc. in October 2011. Linkable Networks, Inc. was founded in 2010 and is headquartered in Boston, Massachusetts.
Detailed Description


