linkable networks inc
Public Company









Company Profile
Sector: Communications
Industry: Media
Sub-Industry: Advertising & Marketing
Linkable Networks, Inc. provides digital advertising services. The Company develops platform that links television, radio, print, banner, text, video, and mobile advertising directly to credit and debit cards. Linkable Networks serves customers in the United States.




